column5: Managed 8 bass and 4 perch from shore this morning.  Lots of fun. Took a pic of this fat little football smallie.
Very nice! You guys are lucky with some good fishing close by that you can get away to for a few hours. Keep the pics coming!
Thats a very nice smallie.....WTG Cudz  Great report and pic Thanks for sharing Leechman
Sorry, I couldn't make it out this morning Chris, looks like you did pretty good!!!!
Nice pic and fish!!!   ... did you forget to wash your face?
